latestPosts.caption:
Ironically, never forgotten 💔 NN
This loss has taught me the most in my life. People come into our lives for a moment, a season or a lifetime. I have always worried about stupid things until I learned to live in the moment and that is what I do more than ever now. I cherish our very short time and albeit it was so complex and difficult, it was the best gift we could have been for each other. 

Always in my heart 🫶🏼🌻🏎️💨
Until we meet again.

Noland Nelson 1981-2021 🕊️♾️🤍

”Love is the only true thing in this universe”
